description: The royal family have come under fire for travelling to Greece during the coronavirus pandemic.
title: Covid: Dutch king expresses regret over Greek holiday scandal
title_page: Covid: Dutch king expresses regret over Greek holiday scandal - BBC News
maintext: The royals flew out on a government plane on Friday and were immediately criticised for going on holiday when the population was being advised to stay at home as much as possible to curb the spread of Covid-19.
